## §7. IMPACT ASSESSMENT

### §7.1 Files affected (dry estimate)

| Category | Count | Risk |
|----------|-------|------|
| `.kris` memory files | ~192 | LOW (chỉ rename) |
| `.khương` files | ~20-50 | LOW (chỉ rename) |
| Code references `.kris` | chưa scan | MEDIUM (cần sed) |
| `nattos.sh` audit script | 1 | LOW (update pattern) |
| SPEC v1.1 document | 1 | LOW (reference cũ) |
| Memory healing logic | chưa scan | MEDIUM |

### §7.2 Risk matrix

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Code dùng `endsWith('.kris')` switch | grep + fix; LAW-2 cấm rồi nên ít |
| `git mv` fail trên file chưa tracked | Fallback sang `mv` + `git add` |
| Audit script v7.0 báo missing sau rename | Update pattern trong nattos.sh |
| Memory loader không tìm thấy file | Update `*.kris` → `*.na` trong loader |

